    "description": "导读：泰莎是一只兔子，受雇于一家服装厂，担任机械师。女主人公穿梭于缝纫室和染色车间等各个部门，修理损坏的机械装置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/e41fa32a38d57f7bfbcefdad9512ae6d.poster.avif?t=1749560906\" width=613 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/e41fa32a38d57f7bfbcefdad9512ae6d.webm?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>我们的小兔子有很多工作要做，所以她会制造机器人并编写程序来帮忙。此外，如果她掉进了死胡同，还可以让时间倒流。<br>每个关卡都是一个小谜题，需要你的批判性思维。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/8a652ce65f1a935827073c25bbc13249.poster.avif?t=1749560906\" width=613 height=691 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/8a652ce65f1a935827073c25bbc13249.webm?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>玩家可以使用编辑器创建自己的工厂地点，并与他人共享。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/66d439664285f36ae02df9fe69a24875.poster.avif?t=1749560906\" width=612 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/66d439664285f36ae02df9fe69a24875.webm?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/66d439664285f36ae02df9fe69a24875.mp4?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>游戏采用了独特的图形风格，其灵感来自阿尔方斯-穆查（Alphonse Mucha）的作品和装饰艺术。它融合了令人联想到兔子洞穴的植物图案和蒸汽朋克风格的蒸汽动力机器，非常引人入胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/60b3fa52bdccfede5787d59920ffc29c.poster.avif?t=1749560906\" width=612 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/60b3fa52bdccfede5787d59920ffc29c.webm?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253650/extras/60b3fa52bdccfede5787d59920ffc29c.mp4?t=1749560906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>我们还为游戏准备了独特的音乐作品，这些乐器反映了主人公所经过的工厂的不同区域。在锅炉房里，你可以清楚地听到蒸汽的声音，而在办公室里，你可以听到笔在会计的羊皮纸上移动的声音。",
